title: Mayhem - Life Eternal - EP [320kpbs]
description:
Life Eternal is an EP from Mayhem . The EP was released on January 7, 2009 and it contains 5 mixes of songs from their album "De Mysteriis Dom Sathanas". It has different vocal styles and the introduction of the song drum Funeral Fog which was cut on the original disk. The EP IS limited to 3000 copies.

Genre: Black Metal

Tracklist: 

1. Cursed in Eternity	  
2. Pagan Fears	    	  
3. Freezing Moon	  
4. Funeral Fog	
5. Life Eternal
